A high-class cafe & bakery brand of crostini. crostini offers a range of European breads, patisserie and coffee. The antique European style setting creates a peaceful ambience for shoppers and diners. Their brand name was inspired by a classic Italian snack, Crostini, which is a grilled bread, seasoned with various ingredients, with a choice of simplicity in the taste.
